metadata.name: World Through My Eyes
metadata.description:
See the world through my eyes
Traversing through space and time
Light lingering through each movement
Reverberations intesify
As they continuously move from one to the next
Colors crashing creating calm chaos
Everything as one
Everything as truth
As above so below
Through it all
A never-ending fall.

---

My homage to the infinite possibilities of inspiration that have been created by the Avril15 project. 

Full screen, sound on, mind open. 

Original video, animation, and sound, with accompanying prose.

---
